            <title><![CDATA[Metaphor: ReFantazio shipments and digital sales top two million]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/metaphor-refantazio-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-two-million</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/metaphor-refantazio-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-two-million.1224447/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div role="main">
  
  <article>

    
<header>

  <div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>One million copies moved since last report.</span>
      </p></div>

  

</header>  

<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p>Total worldwide shipments and digital sales for fantasy <a title="Genres > RPG [17,380 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg">RPG</a> <em><a title="Games > Metaphor: ReFantazio [36 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/metaphor-refantazio">Metaphor: ReFantazio</a></em> have surpassed two million units worldwide as on March 31, 2025, according to a <a href="https://www.segasammy.co.jp/cms/wp-content/uploads/pdf/en/ir/20250618_Management_large_MTG_all_e.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SEGA SAMMY Management Meeting 2025 presentation</a> published on June 18. <span id="more-975163"></span></p><p>The game was <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/10/metaphor-refantazio-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-one-million">last reported</a> to have surpassed one million units, day and date with its release on October 11, 2024. It is available for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,783 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,448 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,112 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,551 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2679460/Metaphor_ReFantazio/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/metaphor-refantazio/9n5dv8310xp7" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>.</p></div>

        
    
  </article>
</div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/metaphor-refantazio-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-two-million]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
